column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "C6CE334042877DD92C97F584E41C4BC4", "Hey guys, if you want to get thru here...")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "208FC68741ECF22A5892479480A3A120", "Long time no see.")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "0F61A6D14872D0786FB907ADC2D866CC", "Mmm. You guys again!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "A126C1834C5307FE2815EDBEC857A035", "That\'s my line! It was so easy to find you. Ready to lose?")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "930FDC644E57DCD6BD4E26B560C72DB7", "Lose? No way! I\'ll show you what I do when I get serious!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "DBF01D84479DB3514926A59AE825187B", "Let\'s settle this once and for all!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "73725C81485086035CD4609BE080ECBF", "How come...I can\'t win?")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "DA2C347944970D43D118BB88973C555A", "What\'s wrong? Aren\'t you going to run?")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "21E8431D499A70D72D951CAA21705723", "I\'m too tired.")
INVTEXT("...")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "8F85F95E4E694DB04A7FCD890C14FF22", "I became a bandit cuz I thought this island was done for, so I just did whatever.")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "46A51731489380BA7324BB90E5228664", "Did you know the island was in trouble?")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "3DB743664DA697F06B8B409AC41291C2", "Yes, then you showed up. I guess it\'s dumb to start helping you now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "CD2716AA42FD030935FEAC834D5F6B1E", "I don\'t think so. Come to the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "5D44CA4D4722A5B8F7EBB7A25906FE48", "No, I can\'t. Plus, I don\'t think anybody would forgive me for what I\'ve done.")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "C5A101D24D1F6FBF0FBC448CD9D16F03", "Oh, just be quiet and come with me!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "7608703F4FE91781986EDFA5607A2F73", "You can be helpful! Everyone has something to offer!")
INVTEXT("!!!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "C7C20FAC4A4B96118DD96B97AC265FE9", "Can this island be saved? You\'re going to save it for us, right?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "0E236B064A89521C9A316CB83587BD6A", "Of course! You know where the city is, right?")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "80BBC95744F54071DED7EAB3CEF4DB49", "Ohhhhh! I\'ll be there!")
NSLOCTEXT("[374CB60C4F670CDBCA640ABFCD2D378E]", "E25CB4644EF29E02E566ABAA2935F4B1", "Ogremon joins the city!")
